data.value:
Vitamilk is a popular soymilk drink in the Philippines made from whole, non-GMO soybeans. It’s high in plant-based protein and often enriched with vitamins and minerals. Available in flavors like original, double choco shake, and energy, it’s marketed as a nutritious beverage for active lifestyles.
Type of Milk: Plant-based soy milk (non-dairy)
Ideal For: Individuals seeking a plant-based alternative to dairy milk Active individuals or athletes due to its high protein content People looking for a nutritious drink enriched with vitamins and minerals
Ingredients: Whole, non-GMO soybeans Water Sugar (depending on flavor) Added vitamins and minerals (such as Calcium, Vitamin D, Vitamin B12)
Storage: Store in a cool, dry place. Once opened, refrigerate and consume within 3-5 days for optimal freshness. ______________________________________________________________________________
Nutrition Facts (Per 250ml Serving): Calories: 140 kcal Protein: 8g Fat: 7g Carbohydrates: 10g Sugar: 7g (may vary depending on flavor) Sodium: 50mg Calcium: 200mg (enriched) Vitamin B12: 0.5mcg (enriched) Iron: 1.5mg (enriched)
